Why Freenove ESP32 S3 Wroom Cam Board over the ESP32, ESP32CAM or ESP8266?
#S3 Wroom over ESP32

#S3 Wroom over ESP32CAM
- Not enough GPIO pins present
- Previously allocated 2 functions on 1 pin which deterred the primary function of the project

#S3 Wroom over ESP8266
- Lack of linear ability to integrate the 








Why PIR Sensor over Ultrasonic Sensor?
- PIR sensor: Best suited for general security, w/ wide area monitoring where people are moving
- Better for lower power consumption

- Ultrasonic sensor

- False triggers can occur; Failsafe mechanism in place, whereby a delay is set in place